Document: PacketPeerStream  
Path: godot/classes/class_packetpeerstream.rst  
Summary: Provides a wrapper for using packets over a stream, enabling packet-based communication with StreamPeers through a custom protocol.  

PacketStreamPeer provides a wrapper for working using packets over a stream. This allows for using packet based code with StreamPeers. PacketPeerStream implements a custom protocol over the StreamPeer, so the user should not read or write to the wrapped StreamPeer directly. Note: When exporting to Android, ensure the INTERNET permission is enabled in the Android export preset to allow network communication.
