Summary: Defines properties for managing input/output buffer sizes and stream peer connections in PacketPeerStream.

- input_buffer_max_size (int): Maximum size of the input buffer. Default: 65532
- output_buffer_max_size (int): Maximum size of the output buffer. Default: 65532
- stream_peer (StreamPeer): Associated stream peer connection (no default value specified)
