Document: PacketPeerStream  
Path: godot/classes/class_packetpeerstream.rst  
Summary: Properties for configuring buffer sizes and the underlying StreamPeer in PacketPeerStream.  

- input_buffer_max_size (int): Maximum size of the input buffer. Default: 65532. Set via set_input_buffer_max_size(value: int), get via get_input_buffer_max_size() → int.  
- output_buffer_max_size (int): Maximum size of the output buffer. Default: 65532. Set via set_output_buffer_max_size(value: int), get via get_output_buffer_max_size() → int.  
- stream_peer (StreamPeer): The wrapped StreamPeer object. Set via set_stream_peer(value: StreamPeer), get via get_stream_peer() → StreamPeer.